      "span_text": "A recent SANS study performed on lipid contrast matched conditions to isolate the scattering coming from the cholesterol inserted in a POPC or POPS liposome, has revealed a molar fraction solubility limit of 61% and 73% of cholesterol in POPC and POPS, respectively."
